<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1" />
  <meta name="color-scheme" content="only light" />
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#fcfcfc" />
  <title>Projects — Your Name</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
 
    :root {
      --bg: #fcfcfc;
      --text: #111;
      --muted: #666;
      --link: #111;
      --link-hover: #555;
      --border: #e5e5e5;
      --font-body: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
      --font-ui: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      --max-width: 680px;
      --side-pad: 2rem;
    }
 
    html, body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.75;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
 
    .page {
      max-width: var(--max-width);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 3rem var(--side-pad) 6rem;
    }
 
    /* Nav */
    nav { margin-bottom: 3.5rem; }
 
    nav ul {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
 
    nav a {
      font-family: var(--font-ui);
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      transition: color 0.15s ease;
    }
 
    nav a:hover { color: var(--text); }
    nav a.active { color: var(--text); }
 
    /* Headings */
    h1 {
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
 
    /* Section intro */
    .intro {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
 
    /* Project sections */
    .project {
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }
 
    .project-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: baseline;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    }
 
    .project-name {
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
 
    .project-name:hover { color: var(--muted); }
 
    .project-url {
      font-family: var(--font-ui);
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
 
    .project-url:hover { color: var(--text); }
 
    .project-desc {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
 
    .project-desc a {
      color: var(--link);
      text-decoration: underline;
      text-underline-offset: 3px;
      text-decoration-thickness: 1px;
      transition: color 0.15s ease;
    }
 
    .project-desc a:hover { color: var(--link-hover); }
 
    /* Divider */
    hr {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      margin: 2.5rem 0;
    }
 
    /* Mini project list */
    .mini-section h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
 
    .mini-list {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.35rem;
    }
 
    .mini-list a {
      font-family: var(--font-ui);
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.15s ease;
    }
 
    .mini-list a:hover { color: var(--muted); }
 
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      :root { --side-pad: 1.25rem; }
      .page { padding-top: 2rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    <nav>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="index.html">About</a></li>
        <li><a href="thoughts.html">Thoughts</a></li>
        <li><a href="projects.html" class="active">Projects</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
 
    <main>
      <h1>Projects</h1>
      <p class="intro">
        Over the years, I've had the privilege of working on diverse projects, from open-source libraries to large-scale applications.
      </p>
 
      <!-- Repeat this block for each major project -->
      <div class="project">
        <div class="project-header">
          <a href="https://example.com" class="project-name" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Project One</a>
          <a href="https://example.com" class="project-url" target="_blank" rel="noopener">example.com</a>
        </div>
        <p class="project-desc">
          Describe what this project is, your role in it, and why it matters. Link to relevant resources like <a href="https://github.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">the repository</a> or a blog post about it.
        </p>
      </div>
 
      <div class="project">
        <div class="project-header">
          <a href="https://example.com" class="project-name" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Project Two</a>
          <a href="https://example.com" class="project-url" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github.com/you/project-two</a>
        </div>
        <p class="project-desc">
          Another major project. Explain the problem it solves and highlight notable contributions or outcomes you're proud of.
        </p>
      </div>
 
      <div class="project">
        <div class="project-header">
          <a href="https://example.com" class="project-name" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Project Three</a>
        </div>
        <p class="project-desc">
          A third project. Keep descriptions focused — the goal is to give a clear picture of the work without over-explaining.
        </p>
      </div>
 
      <hr />
 
      <div class="mini-section">
        <h2>Fun &amp; experimental projects</h2>
        <ul class="mini-list">
          <li><a href="https://example.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Side Project Alpha</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://example.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Side Project Beta</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://example.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Side Project Gamma</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
 
      <hr />
 
      <div class="mini-section">
        <h2>Mini projects</h2>
        <ul class="mini-list">
          <li><a href="https://example.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mini Project 1</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://example.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mini Project 2</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://example.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mini Project 3</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
 
